1
00:01:07,800 --> 00:01:10,080
You have nothing to worry about.

2
00:01:18,320 --> 00:01:19,650
The wedding date is set.

3
00:01:20,520 --> 00:01:23,600
But I still have something to ask you.

4
00:01:25,000 --> 00:01:29,160
Why did you slander Ji's reputation before?

5
00:01:29,840 --> 00:01:31,600
Nothing happened.

6
00:01:32,000 --> 00:01:34,720
Yet you claimed he forced himself on you.

7
00:01:37,920 --> 00:01:39,720
Zhaoxue.

8
00:01:40,920 --> 00:01:42,720
Zhaoxue.

9
00:01:47,360 --> 00:01:48,160
I'm here.

10
00:01:53,360 --> 00:01:54,840
Lord Fang.

11
00:01:55,080 --> 00:01:56,640
Men and women should keep their distance.

12
00:01:56,640 --> 00:02:00,080
I appreciate your kindness on Ji's behalf, Miss Gu.

13
00:02:01,280 --> 00:02:03,040
I will look after him tonight.

14
00:02:04,240 --> 00:02:06,640
You should go back and rest.

15
00:02:36,560 --> 00:02:37,840
Because I knew

16
00:02:38,040 --> 00:02:39,240
that with my sister's temperament,

17
00:02:39,240 --> 00:02:41,440
she would never agree to this marriage.

18
00:02:41,440 --> 00:02:43,240
That is why I resorted to this.

19
00:02:45,600 --> 00:02:47,600
As for you and your sister's background,

20
00:02:47,600 --> 00:02:50,040
I have already investigated it thoroughly.

21
00:02:50,040 --> 00:02:53,560
I didn't expose it for the sake of Ji'er's reputation.

22
00:02:55,440 --> 00:02:57,640
I address you as Second Miss,

23
00:02:59,040 --> 00:03:03,120
and I hope you will respect your own dignity.

24
00:03:04,560 --> 00:03:06,640
Do not bring those tricks learned in the brothels,

25
00:03:06,640 --> 00:03:08,200
those low-class habits,

26
00:03:08,200 --> 00:03:09,400
into the Fang family.

27
00:03:12,000 --> 00:03:14,320
Letting you marry into the Fang family as a concubine

28
00:03:14,320 --> 00:03:16,320
is merely due to the circumstances.

29
00:03:16,960 --> 00:03:18,440
I also hope, Second Miss,

30
00:03:20,320 --> 00:03:22,400
that you know your place.

31
00:03:24,440 --> 00:03:25,400
I understand.

32
00:03:27,040 --> 00:03:28,570
Thank you, Prime Minister.

33
00:03:38,920 --> 00:03:39,760
Sister.

34
00:03:42,520 --> 00:03:43,320
Yan'er.

35
00:03:44,600 --> 00:03:46,600
I'm marrying Lord Fang today.

36
00:03:46,800 --> 00:03:48,760
I specifically asked the Prime Minister.

37
00:03:48,760 --> 00:03:49,640
Since the eldest sister is like a mother,

38
00:03:49,640 --> 00:03:51,170
I want you to sit as my elder.

39
00:03:53,560 --> 00:03:54,360
Sister.

40
00:03:55,840 --> 00:03:56,900
Congratulations.

41
00:03:57,720 --> 00:03:59,050
You got what you wanted.

42
00:04:00,600 --> 00:04:01,720
However,

43
00:04:05,040 --> 00:04:06,320
Fang Ji is a good man,

44
00:04:07,440 --> 00:04:09,570
but you're only becoming a concubine.

45
00:04:10,200 --> 00:04:12,060
Do you really think it's worth it?

46
00:04:12,560 --> 00:04:13,560
Of course it is.

47
00:04:14,880 --> 00:04:15,680
Sister,

48
00:04:16,920 --> 00:04:20,320
if this is truly what you want,

49
00:04:22,000 --> 00:04:23,530
then I give you my blessing.

50
00:04:23,760 --> 00:04:24,600
Really?

51
00:05:24,480 --> 00:05:27,480
First bow to Heaven and Earth.

52
00:06:19,800 --> 00:06:21,000
Look.

53
00:06:21,000 --> 00:06:23,720
The groom is using a rooster for the ceremony.

54
00:06:27,080 --> 00:06:28,360
It doesn't matter.

55
00:06:28,360 --> 00:06:30,760
It's just a concubine entering the family.

56
00:06:31,160 --> 00:06:32,320
I heard

57
00:06:32,320 --> 00:06:34,560
this marriage is just to ward off bad luck.

58
00:06:34,560 --> 00:06:38,120
Don't you know the bride is from Qihong Tower?

59
00:06:38,720 --> 00:06:40,520
She doesn't know her place.

60
00:06:40,800 --> 00:06:43,080
Dreaming of a formal wedding into the Prime Minister's Manor.

61
00:06:43,080 --> 00:06:44,280
Exactly. She doesn't know where she stands.

62
00:06:44,280 --> 00:06:46,080
If you dare talk nonsense again,

63
00:06:46,080 --> 00:06:47,540
I'll rip your tongues out.

64
00:06:48,320 --> 00:06:51,840
Who are you to talk to me like that?

65
00:06:58,080 --> 00:06:59,360
Longying Guard.

66
00:07:00,440 --> 00:07:01,840
Spare us, my Lady!

67
00:07:01,920 --> 00:07:02,560
I was wrong.

68
00:07:02,560 --> 00:07:03,320
Please spare us!

69
00:07:03,320 --> 00:07:03,480
Spare me.

70
00:07:03,480 --> 00:07:07,040
Spare me, My Lord.

71
00:07:07,360 --> 00:07:08,120
Spare my life, My Lord.

72
00:07:08,120 --> 00:07:08,920
Let it go.

73
00:07:11,840 --> 00:07:12,720
Stand up.

74
00:07:13,640 --> 00:07:14,760
Thank you, My Lord.

75
00:07:26,080 --> 00:07:27,640
Husband, you're awake.

76
00:07:32,280 --> 00:07:33,640
Congratulations, Prime Minister.

77
00:07:33,640 --> 00:07:35,760
Lord Fang's pulse is stable now.

78
00:07:35,760 --> 00:07:38,080
He will be fine after a night's rest.

79
00:07:40,080 --> 00:07:41,480
What on earth is going on?

80
00:07:42,280 --> 00:07:46,040
Ji'er, is it really that miraculous?

81
00:07:46,360 --> 00:07:49,080
Yan'er is truly your lucky star.

82
00:07:49,400 --> 00:07:52,080
Yan'er, after we return to the capital,

83
00:07:52,080 --> 00:07:54,080
I will remove your slave status.

84
00:07:54,360 --> 00:07:57,080
I may even make you a co-wife.

85
00:07:57,560 --> 00:07:58,480
I wouldn't dare.

86
00:07:58,480 --> 00:08:00,040
As long as Lord Fang recovers,

87
00:08:00,040 --> 00:08:02,080
I will be content.

88
00:08:10,760 --> 00:08:12,290
What are you talking about?

89
00:08:37,159 --> 00:08:38,289
What's on your mind?

90
00:08:39,480 --> 00:08:41,080
Look at these lotus flowers.

91
00:08:42,080 --> 00:08:44,080
They're blooming beautifully.

92
00:08:47,040 --> 00:08:48,100
Yan'er is married.

93
00:08:49,840 --> 00:08:52,840
I've finally done right by my parents.

94
00:08:57,440 --> 00:08:58,840
Fang Ji is awake.

95
00:08:59,200 --> 00:09:00,530
Do you want to go see him?

96
00:09:06,400 --> 00:09:07,480
Forget it.

97
00:09:08,960 --> 00:09:09,840
As long as

98
00:09:11,200 --> 00:09:12,730
he's awake, that's enough.

99
00:09:16,640 --> 00:09:18,160
I won't marry her.

100
00:09:20,040 --> 00:09:21,640
What 'warding off bad luck'?

101
00:09:21,800 --> 00:09:22,960
It's ridiculous.

102
00:09:23,400 --> 00:09:25,040
Ji'er.

103
00:09:25,040 --> 00:09:27,400
I've already registered your marriage.

104
00:09:27,600 --> 00:09:28,930
You don't want to marry?

105
00:09:29,560 --> 00:09:30,480
It's too late.

106
00:09:30,880 --> 00:09:32,140
Then I'll divorce her.

107
00:09:32,800 --> 00:09:34,400
My heart belongs to another.

108
00:09:34,560 --> 00:09:36,820
I won't marry anyone but her in this life.

109
00:09:38,560 --> 00:09:39,960
Unless I'm dead.

110
00:09:53,480 --> 00:09:56,880
Since they're already married anyway,

111
00:09:57,480 --> 00:09:59,080
when we return to the capital,

112
00:09:59,080 --> 00:10:00,810
I'll take you to meet my father.

113
00:10:01,200 --> 00:10:04,080
I promise to marry you with a grand ceremony.

114
00:10:07,680 --> 00:10:08,560
Young Marquis.

115
00:10:14,560 --> 00:10:15,690
I'm sorry, Zhaoxue.

116
00:10:16,960 --> 00:10:19,000
I was too impatient.

117
00:10:26,280 --> 00:10:28,280
This is my personal seal.

118
00:10:28,640 --> 00:10:30,840
You can use it to command the Dragon Shadow Guard.

119
00:10:30,840 --> 00:10:33,880
Since you'll be the Marchioness one day,

120
00:10:34,560 --> 00:10:36,620
you'll have to keep this seal anyway.

121
00:10:38,600 --> 00:10:39,360
Here.

122
00:11:22,320 --> 00:11:22,800
Stop it.

123
00:11:29,960 --> 00:11:30,490
Zhaoxue.

124
00:11:38,480 --> 00:11:40,680
I never thought you could be so vicious.

125
00:11:44,160 --> 00:11:46,560
Sister, it's windy out here.

126
00:11:46,880 --> 00:11:48,680
I'm worried you'll catch a cold.

127
00:11:52,280 --> 00:11:53,160
Lord Fang.

128
00:11:54,200 --> 00:11:56,530
Why are you speaking so harshly to Yan'er?

129
00:11:59,080 --> 00:12:01,010
Now that you are married to Yan'er,

130
00:12:01,600 --> 00:12:05,800
I hope you will respect and protect her.

131
00:12:16,960 --> 00:12:18,760
If you dare lay a finger on her,

132
00:12:19,480 --> 00:12:20,880
I will make you pay.

133
00:12:21,200 --> 00:12:23,200
Is that clear?

134
00:12:40,800 --> 00:12:41,760
Zhaoxue.

135
00:12:47,280 --> 00:12:48,410
Did you catch a cold?

136
00:12:49,040 --> 00:12:49,920
Lord Fang.

137
00:12:56,640 --> 00:12:59,080
Is this waist token yours?

138
00:13:05,240 --> 00:13:06,240
Why do you have it?

139
00:13:07,760 --> 00:13:08,960
I found it in the fire.

140
00:13:11,200 --> 00:13:13,920
It seems she wants to frame me.

141
00:13:16,720 --> 00:13:17,250
Zhaoxue.

142
00:13:18,560 --> 00:13:19,360
At this point,

143
00:13:19,920 --> 00:13:21,650
do you still not know who she is?

144
00:13:22,600 --> 00:13:23,530
What do you mean?

145
00:13:24,800 --> 00:13:27,360
I'm talking about your sister, Su Qingyan.

146
00:13:33,640 --> 00:13:35,170
Have you ever thought about

147
00:13:35,360 --> 00:13:37,360
since she came to us,

148
00:13:37,440 --> 00:13:39,800
how many strange things have happened?

149
00:13:40,320 --> 00:13:42,000
While I was in a coma,

150
00:13:42,200 --> 00:13:45,120
how did she bewitch my father

151
00:13:45,240 --> 00:13:46,640
and force me to marry her?

152
00:13:47,400 --> 00:13:50,400
And that Daoist Master Miaoxu who suddenly appeared.

153
00:13:55,640 --> 00:13:56,920
Believe it or not,

154
00:13:57,720 --> 00:14:00,920
last night I saw with my own eyes that she tried to kill you.

155
00:14:01,520 --> 00:14:02,360
Impossible.

156
00:14:04,520 --> 00:14:05,520
It's impossible.

157
00:14:07,720 --> 00:14:09,720
Zhaoxue, at a time like this,

158
00:14:09,720 --> 00:14:10,780
you need to wake up.

159
00:14:23,920 --> 00:14:26,240
A glimpse of misty rain, a fleeting dream.
